    when "Table7A-example1"
      | #[b Is] talamh maith anois é.
    when "Table7A-example2"
      | Ealaíontóir maith #[b is] ea ise.
    when "Table7A-example3"
      | #[b Ní] bia bainne is #[b ní] bainne bláthach.
    when "Table7A-example4"
      | #[b Ní] hé a d&rsquo;inis an bhréag sin.
    when "Table7A-example5"
      | #[b An] í Bríd an múinteoir?
    when "Table7A-example6"
      | #[b An] fada go dtiocfaidh sé?
    when "Table7A-example7"
